{"tid":467190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"23歲女工作問題困擾　新清水灣道跳橋亡","createTime":"2017-11-13T09:29:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T09:47:10.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8610a08d89cf5c1d69eda1435efe8455ed0c1b95","tid":467190,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171113/photo/bkn-20171113132445237-1113_00822_001_03p.jpg?20171113163936\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171113%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171113132445237-1113_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20171113163936&h=d2ef80dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">女子自天橋直墮馬路。(趙瑞麟攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n新清水灣道天橋又添亡魂，中午12時許，一名姓曾（23歲）女子，自秀茂坪順利紀律部隊宿舍對開新清水灣道天橋墮下，直墮50米跌落往順利邨方向行車線路面，一輛的士剛巧駛至，司機見狀已扭軚閃避，惟左邊車頭仍將女子撞及。<br />\n<br />\n救護員接報到場，證實女子已氣絕死亡。警方一度將該段馬路封閉調查。現場未有檢獲遺書，經初步調查後，相信事件沒有可疑，死者死因有待驗屍確定。據了解，曾受工作問題困擾。<br />\n<br />\n根據資料，新清水灣道天橋曾發生多宗跳橋悲劇。去年2月，一名不堪長期失業的姓余（32歲）男子，亦在上址天橋跳下身亡。2015年2月，一名中年男子在天橋跨欄墮下斃命。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171113/bkn-20171113132445237-1113_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171113%2Fbkn-20171113132445237-1113_00822_001.html&d=%2FYMK0%2FgWmQ5%2F85T3GOZOdS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=9229323d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171113/bkn-20171113132445237-1113_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c7be6385db1b902bf2b3e24f21a651d372ee29ac","tid":467190,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:30:33.000Z","msg":"清水灣道天橋墮下，直墮50米跌落往順利邨方向行車線路面，一輛的士剛巧駛至，司機見狀已扭軚閃避，惟左邊車頭仍將女子撞及。<br />\n<br />\n個司機應該成世有個陰影係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661a5ca9ba4e51ea77629504fb4eadc66ee0c85b","tid":467190,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:31:36.000Z","msg":"23歲..點解唔俾我..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係唔好鳩嗡<br />\n一陣返黎搵我"},{"pid":"2ca74676c4ae15093881deeea23b751f042efcc7","tid":467190,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>23歲..點解唔俾我..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係唔好鳩嗡<br />\n一陣返黎搵我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/173436_8f56bc4bd10cfa86f6f3c799c7e51aa4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F173436_8f56bc4bd10cfa86f6f3c799c7e51aa4.jpg&h=c8e4eb63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09294dc14b6705c89d423df0be270fa050a87bd6","tid":467190,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:37:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6aaa748f7fe9fd1b7d9607e5fced4157a3555a68","tid":467190,"uid":12720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:39:35.000Z","msg":"司機會唔會比人告??"},{"pid":"c57d023175755e24c1b36ef7815ff3f165b354a4","tid":467190,"uid":37505,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T09:47:10.000Z","msg":"臭閪死都要害人"}]}